<li id="cite_note-20"><b><a href="#cite_ref-20" title="">^</a></b> Whitted, K.S. (2005). <a href="http://proquest.umi.com/pqdlink?Ver=1&amp;Exp=12-10-2012&amp;FMT=7&amp;DID=990282831&amp;RQT=309&amp;attempt=1" class="external text" title="http://proquest.umi.com/pqdlink?Ver=1&amp;Exp=12-10-2012&amp;FMT=7&amp;DID=990282831&amp;RQT=309&amp;attempt=1" rel="nofollow"><i>Student reports of physical and psychological maltreatment in schools: An under-explored aspect of student victimization in schools.</i></a> University of Tennessee.</li>
