<li id="cite_note-22"><b><a href="#cite_ref-22" title="">^</a></b> Vossekuil, B., Reddy, M., Fein, R.; Borum, R.; &amp; Modzeleski, W. (2000). <a href="http://www.ustreas.gov/usss/ntac/ntac_ssi_report.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.ustreas.gov/usss/ntac/ntac_ssi_report.pdf" rel="nofollow">USSS Safe School Initiative: An Interim Report on the Prevention of Targeted Violence in Schools</a>, Washington, DC: US Secret Service National Threat Assessment Center.</li>
<li id="cite_note-23"><b><a href="#cite_ref-23" title="">^</a></b> Brownstein, A. <a href="http://www.thefreelibrary.com/The+bully+pulpit:+post-Columbine+harassment+victims+take+schools+to...-a097175612" class="external text" title="http://www.thefreelibrary.com/The+bully+pulpit:+post-Columbine+harassment+victims+take+schools+to...-a097175612" rel="nofollow">The Bully Pulpit: Post-Columbine, Harassment Victims Take School To Court.</a> <i>TRIAL - the Journal of the Association of Trial Lawyers of America</i>, December 2002.</li>
<li id="cite_note-namiedef-24"><b><a href="#cite_ref-namiedef_24-0" title="">^</a></b> Namie, Gary and Ruth <a href="http://www.bullyinginstitute.org/education/bbstudies/def.html" class="external text" title="http://www.bullyinginstitute.org/education/bbstudies/def.html" rel="nofollow">Workplace Bullying Institute Definition</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-cyber2-25"><b><a href="#cite_ref-cyber2_25-0" title="">^</a></b> <i>Belsey, W <a href="http://www.cyberbullying.ca/pdf/Cyberbullying_Article_by_Bill_Belsey.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.cyberbullying.ca/pdf/Cyberbullying_Article_by_Bill_Belsey.pdf" rel="nofollow">Cyberbullying: An Emerging Threat to the Always On Generation</a></i></li>
<li id="cite_note-cyber-26"><b><a href="#cite_ref-cyber_26-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFPage.2C_Chris2006">Page, Chris (2006-04-16). <a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/4912766.stm" class="external text" title="http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/4912766.stm" rel="nofollow">"Striking back at the cyberbullies"</a>. BBC News<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/4912766.stm" class="external free" title="http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/4912766.stm" rel="nofollow">http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/4912766.stm</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2009-03-22</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Striking+back+at+the+cyberbullies&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Page%2C+Chris&amp;rft.au=Page%2C+Chris&amp;rft.date=2006-04-16&amp;rft.pub=BBC+News&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.bbc.co.uk%2F1%2Fhi%2Fuk%2F4912766.stm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Bullying"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-mod-27"><b><a href="#cite_ref-mod_27-0" title="">^</a></b> <i>The Values and Standards of the British Army – A Guide to Soldiers</i>, Ministry of Defence, UK March 2000, paragraph 23.</li>
<li id="cite_note-28"><b><a href="#cite_ref-28" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.deepcutreview.org.uk/Home/home/Home" class="external text" title="http://www.deepcutreview.org.uk/Home/home/Home" rel="nofollow">Deepcut Review</a> accessed 14 Jan 07</li>
<li id="cite_note-diff-29"><b><a href="#cite_ref-diff_29-0" title="">^</a></b> <i>Social Psychology of the Individual Soldier</i>, Jean M. Callaghan and Franz Kernic 2003 Armed Forces and International Security: Global Trends and Issues, Lit Verlag, Munster</li>
<li id="cite_note-bbcmil-30"><b><a href="#cite_ref-bbcmil_30-0" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/4477960.stm" class="external text" title="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/4477960.stm" rel="nofollow"><i>Military bullying a global problem</i></a>, BBC, UK Monday, 28 November 2005</li>
